## Pattern Library Established

### 1. Loading Pattern
```typescript
if (loading) {
  return <SkeletonTable rows={5} columns={7} />;
}
```

### 2. Error Pattern
```typescript
if (error) {
  return <ErrorState message={error} onRetry={fetchData} />;
}
```

### 3. Empty Pattern
```typescript
if (data.length === 0) {
  return <EmptyState icon="..." title="..." description="..." />;
}
```

### 4. Toast Pattern
```typescript
try {
  const data = await saveData();
  showSuccess('Data saved successfully');
} catch (err) {
  showError('Failed to save. Please try again.');
}
```

### 5. Submitting Pattern
```typescript
const [submitting, setSubmitting] = useState(false);

onClick={async () => {
  setSubmitting(true);
  try { await save(); } finally { setSubmitting(false); }
}}
disabled={submitting}
```

